Package: Repliscope
Type: Package
Language: en-GB
Title: Create, Plot and Compare Replication Timing Profiles
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Dzmitry G Batrakou
Maintainer: Dzmitry G Batrakou <d.batrakou@gmail.com>
Description: Repliscope is a package to load and analyse bed-formatted read counts,  
    create ratio of read counts from replicating to non-replicating samples, normalise
    the ratio and plot the resulting replication timing profile. It also allows comparison
    of two replication profiles using z-score statistics. The package also comes with 
	interactive	Shiny app.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Depends:
	R (>= 2.10),
	ggplot2,
	shiny
Imports:
	stats,
	utils,
	grDevices,
	colourpicker
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
